>\n符合晒呢三種條件 SB2可以一戰<br />\n如果唔係求其一部平啲價位既都屌打<br />\n利申SB2用家 快樂使用中"},{"pid":"f3b9006a9c617be42ee68c6dd485650bcb359451","tid":478097,"uid":36880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T04:35:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f01af510edf4dfe609a13bf9593153d920add6fa","tid":478097,"uid":73731,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T04:43:15.000Z","msg":"算啦apple電腦比古人用<br />\n唔講其他，齋touch mon都吊打macbook啦"},{"pid":"669e77a01af8eb09b8cb59f999fef9c4461e1e0a","tid":478097,"uid":56260,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T06:22:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>算啦apple電腦比古人用<br />\n唔講其他，齋touch mon都吊打macbook啦</blockquote><br />\n公道啲講 macOS都有佢好既地方<br />\n無敵既trackpad 目前仲未係notebook可以相提並論<br />\n令到mac係日常既操控上更intuitive<br />\n例如3隻手指做drag、2隻手指double tap可以放大縮細<br />\n另外一般key combo既距離都比windows短<br />\n唔會啲掣放到離行離列 (例如cap screen、quit app等)<br />\n呢啲微細位一日重覆幾百次 已經減輕好多瑣碎既操作<br />\n<br />\n不過呢啲一切都係老本<br />\n只可以話呢兩三年既新macbook真係不思進取<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7a1f819c032dc29a0746cc0cefb8f920122d626","tid":478097,"uid":157453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T08:11:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>算啦apple電腦比古人用<br />\n唔講其他，齋touch mon都吊打macbook啦</blockquote><br />\n公道啲講 macOS都有佢好既地方<br />\n無敵既trackpad 目前仲未係notebook可以相提並論<br />\n令到mac係日常既操控上更intuitive<br />\n例如3隻手指做drag、2隻手指double tap可以放大縮細<br />\n另外一般key combo既距離都比windows短<br />\n唔會啲掣放到離行離列 (例如cap screen、quit app等)<br />\n呢啲微細位一日重覆幾百次 已經減輕好多瑣碎既操作<br />\n<br />\n不過呢啲一切都係老本<br />\n只可以話呢兩三年既新macbook真係不思進取<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n仲飲緊奶嘅時候已經話win for 打機；mac for 剪片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 其實點解？"},{"pid":"904be3f3c6ce99dd70ae231d10fe8b50d9ebb290","tid":478097,"uid":33176,"like"